0:03:03.640,0:03:11.260
Before I married my wife, I was brought up in a Christian home

0:03:11.260,0:03:15.100
and always tried to follow the laws of God.

0:03:15.100,0:03:19.000
I prepared myself for this marriage.

0:03:19.000,0:03:22.080
There were many women and girls around me

0:03:22.080,0:03:29.840
but I separated myself from them for one year in order to look for a good partner.

0:03:29.840,0:03:32.540
I remembered this fine, beautiful lady over here.

0:03:32.540,0:03:37.620
I decided to give her a phone call.

0:03:37.620,0:03:43.720
I called her for the first time and asked her, "Will you marry me? Can you be my wife?"

0:03:43.720,0:03:49.920
I married my wife and trouble started.

0:03:49.920,0:03:57.500
At the time, my wife was just a young lady; she had just finished secondary school.

0:03:57.500,0:04:05.740
As we moved into our house, she would be on social media, always with her phone - busy.

0:04:05.740,0:04:11.020
She had no time for me and I talked to her about it.

0:04:11.020,0:04:21.340
I asked her to leave the phone for some time so we could talk and reason as husband and wife.

0:04:21.340,0:04:25.960
I begged her but she refused to listen.

0:04:25.960,0:04:31.280
I told her that what she was doing, I also knew how to do it very well.

0:04:31.280,0:04:35.600
If I started my own, it would be fire.

0:04:35.600,0:04:41.680
She refused; I gave her time to stop but she refused so then, I started my own.

0:04:41.680,0:04:47.680
I brought out my new phone, downloaded WhatsApp, social media and Facebook.

0:04:47.680,0:04:54.940
See friend requests from ladies - fine ones.

0:04:54.940,0:04:57.960
As I started my own, it became fire.

0:04:57.960,0:05:01.260
Nobody was listening to each other anymore.

0:05:01.260,0:05:03.860
Ok, let me forget that one.

0:05:03.860,0:05:06.520
This happened immediately after we got married.

0:05:06.520,0:05:08.240
More especially this year.

0:05:08.240,0:05:14.540
That's when I developed another habit of drinking alcohol.

0:05:14.540,0:05:24.900
What caused that was too much disrespect - beating me in the sense that I could not talk.

0:05:24.900,0:05:28.740
If I talked once, she would reply me twenty times.

0:05:28.740,0:05:37.040
If I tried to calm her down as a husband and come near her to ask what the problem was,

0:05:37.040,0:05:40.580
she would slap me.

0:05:40.580,0:05:45.980
I thank God for being in The SCOAN today because I have been yearning to come here

0:05:45.980,0:05:50.160
because I knew the man of God was the only one who could solve this problem.

0:05:50.160,0:05:52.300
I thank God for what happened last Sunday.

0:05:52.300,0:05:57.160
After the prophecy, I'm very happy with my wife.

0:05:57.160,0:06:01.940
Yesterday as we were walking, she held my hand.

