0:07:42.220,0:07:46.520
I can't see myself standing here. For what now?"

0:07:46.520,0:07:51.520
I don't know what made me to just carry my bag.

0:07:51.520,0:07:55.980
The two couples sitting next to me - they were big, heavy -

0:07:55.980,0:07:58.300
