0:08:40.380,0:08:43.220
And then I realised, truly, I wasn't normal

0:08:43.220,0:08:48.420
because I had a spiritual husband, which I knew.

0:08:48.420,0:08:51.180
I kept praying.

0:08:51.180,0:08:55.560
I thank God that after everything, I came here and I was delivered.

0:08:55.560,0:08:57.320
Praise be to the Lord Jesus!

